   <Ritual>
      <Nerangs id="ritualNerangs">
         <ab>Y52.1 Var. a (mss. 6, 40):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            <em>yaθā ahū vairiiō</em>. dō guftan ud bōy ō ī ātaxš dādan fraharašn ruwān gyān kardan</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "They should recite two <em>yaθā ahū vairiiō</em>. He (the <em>rāspīg</em>) should give <em>bōy</em> to the fire. They should reckon the <em>frauuaṣ̌i</em>, the souls and the spirits."</ab>
         <ab>Y52.1 Var. b (ms. 88):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            <em>yaθā ahū vairiiō</em>. dō guftan ud bōy ō ī ātaxš  dādan  ‡ēč-at‡ anāstārīh ēn gyāg kunišn fraharašn ruwān gyān kardan</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            They should recite two <em>yaθā ahū vairiiō</em>. He (the <em>rāspīg</em>) should give <em>bōy</em> to the fire. They should make at this passage repentance of the sins
            and reckon the <em>frauuaṣ̌i</em>, the souls and the spirits."</ab>
      </Nerangs>
   </Ritual>
